      <title>哥伦比亚立法者寻求削减令市场恐慌的法案成本</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-24/colombia-lawmakers-seek-to-cut-cost-of-bill-that-spooked-markets</link>
